# Liabilities Deposits Offset Account Amount

## identifier
de14912

## type
float

## definition
The gross deposit balance in deposit accounts that are offset against the balance of an outstanding loan when calculating the interest owing.

## guidance
Exclude accounts with no credit outstanding associated with them, and all-in-one facilities where it is not possible to separate the loan balance from the borrower's deposits.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Deposits.OffsetAccount.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo6.02.18
- period=instant
